  "text": "Despite the lack of rigorous results, BP is widely understood to find good solutions (solutions with near-maximal likelihood) in practice. We study BP for blocks of equal size only, however note that recent work have successfully adapted BP to block models with unequal group sizes [CITATION_1] .",
